{"tid":1031842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹女大生脫衣自慰拍片瘋傳　尺度大到嚇壞鄉民","createTime":"2019-02-22T02:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T23:54:24.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"54c4a05fbd2a47dfa590f52995d97dae4541ff02","tid":1031842,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"泰國清邁一名自稱是日泰混血的正妹女大生，日前在網路上公開一則短片，但影片的內容尺度相當大膽，大到讓許多鄉民都被嚇壞。<br />\n<br />\n據泰國《khaosod》報導，這名女大生自稱21歲，就讀清邁某大學名校4年級，但之後卻開始進行脫衣秀，甚至開始自慰，在鏡頭前撥弄下體，尺度極盡風騷淫穢。許多網友看到後，都紛紛譴責該名女生，認為這樣的行為相當不妥，也破壞該校的名譽。警方獲報後已展開調查，外界推測女生可能要博取網友點閱率來賺錢，才出此下策，而主要流出這段影片的臉書頁面，也遭到關閉。<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190222/1521677/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190222%2F1521677%2F&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=df976335\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190222%2F1521677%2F&h=e20b9207\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190222/1521677/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190222/640_a8ef700c2ea3bd95c512ad0560cc6e9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190222%2F640_a8ef700c2ea3bd95c512ad0560cc6e9f.jpg&h=65cff7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190222/640_ee73e0bde0469766a7fdef9677dd7698.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190222%2F640_ee73e0bde0469766a7fdef9677dd7698.jpg&h=afc9cb86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190222/640_82e8b4749c62926a3e2c61aa806b7aa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190222%2F640_82e8b4749c62926a3e2c61aa806b7aa3.jpg&h=7aca3309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br